1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:08,000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

2
00:01:02,540 --> 00:01:04,000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

3
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:07,980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

4
00:01:08,020 --> 00:01:11,140
[Episode 13]

5
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:35,820
I was a bit distracted just now.

6
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:37,490
Sorry about that.

7
00:01:38,790 --> 00:01:39,330
Alright.

8
00:01:40,480 --> 00:01:41,130
Well,

9
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:43,770
how did you know I was looking for someone?

10
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:46,290
I'm sharp as a tack

11
00:01:46,310 --> 00:01:47,180
and always well-informed.

12
00:01:49,950 --> 00:01:52,180
You're the new disciple from Zhuiyu Peak, right?

13
00:01:53,310 --> 00:01:54,570
I heard you have lots of snacks.

14
00:01:55,510 --> 00:01:56,130
Do you have any left?

15
00:01:56,310 --> 00:01:57,260
Share some with me.

16
00:01:58,560 --> 00:01:59,130
Um...

17
00:01:59,710 --> 00:02:00,380
Lifei.

18
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:03,900
I've given them all out today.

19
00:02:04,070 --> 00:02:04,900
I'll bring some for you next time.

20
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:08,130
Remember to save some for me next time!

21
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:09,500
Remember my name!

22
00:02:09,750 --> 00:02:12,730
I'm Deng Xiguang!

23
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:23,570
I've searched all sixteen peaks.

24
00:02:27,870 --> 00:02:28,890
Senior Brother!

25
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,850
Where are you?

26
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:32,570
Coming!

27
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,130
What's wrong?

28
00:02:38,190 --> 00:02:39,540
Someone has broken the restriction spell.

29
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:41,130
Zhaomin wants us to search

30
00:02:41,150 --> 00:02:42,220
for the intruder.

31
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,340
Restriction spell?

32
00:02:57,030 --> 00:02:57,660
Lifei.

33
00:03:01,470 --> 00:03:02,170
Senior brothers!

34
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:03,380
The intruder is here!

35
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:04,130
Senior brothers.

36
00:03:04,750 --> 00:03:05,610
The intruder is here!

37
00:03:05,870 --> 00:03:06,500
Senior brothers!

38
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:07,260
The intruder is here!

39
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:08,940
The records of disciples' origins from all peaks

40
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:09,940
are kept in the Huanyue Shrine

41
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:10,610
behind Wengu Hall.

42
00:03:10,870 --> 00:03:11,690
I'll wait for you there.

43
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:16,690
Lifei!

44
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:18,610
Lifei,

45
00:03:19,190 --> 00:03:20,060
where's the intruder?

46
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:22,380
My mistake.

47
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:23,220
It was a cricket.

48
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:25,060
Go back to your duties.

49
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,060
Go... go catch the intruder.

50
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:27,660
- Go ahead. - Let's go.

51
00:04:19,630 --> 00:04:20,730
You're always running around.

52
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,610
Getting lost elsewhere is one thing.

53
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,610
But if you get lost near Wengu Hall,

54
00:04:24,950 --> 00:04:26,100
the night winds there

55
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:28,170
might kill you because they're colder than winter frost.

56
00:04:28,430 --> 00:04:29,490
Even the guards won't go there.

57
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,930
Only a fool would wait all night.

58
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:37,900
He's no fool.

59
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,220
He must have left.

60
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:34,250
Another pity play. I don't believe it.

61
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:06,250
Huanyue Shrine is a restricted area for the sect.

62
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:07,980
Unauthorized disciples are not allowed to enter.

63
00:06:09,630 --> 00:06:10,490
Senior brothers,

64
00:06:11,510 --> 00:06:12,980
I'm here on my master's orders.

65
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:14,540
I need to look up some sect records.

66
00:06:14,950 --> 00:06:16,700
Oh, you're from Cuihua Peak.

67
00:06:17,430 --> 00:06:18,050
Senior sister,

68
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:19,930
did Qin send you?

69
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:22,610
Yes, him.

70
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,490
Then it's fine.

71
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:25,170
Please come in.

72
00:06:25,830 --> 00:06:26,490
Please.

73
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:40,810
Who's there?

74
00:07:55,950 --> 00:07:58,050
Hushe Peak.

75
00:07:59,630 --> 00:08:00,660
Hushe Peak?

76
00:08:26,510 --> 00:08:27,340
What are you doing here again?

77
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:28,930
If you really want to make it up to me,

78
00:08:28,950 --> 00:08:30,100
just stay out of my sight.

79
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,460
I still have something to finish.

80
00:08:36,550 --> 00:08:37,580
What are you plotting now?

81
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:40,850
Trust me one more time.

82
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,370
Trust you, my foot.

83
00:08:43,670 --> 00:08:44,420
Stop following me.

84
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:52,010
If we're caught,

85
00:08:52,390 --> 00:08:53,730
we'll both be expelled from Wuyue Court.

86
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:09,060
Forget it.

87
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:09,940
I'm going back.

88
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:11,650
Your master already knows.

89
00:11:11,790 --> 00:11:12,730
Take care of yourself.

90
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:34,850
Master.

91
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:37,060
You truly are exceptionally gifted.

92
00:11:37,630 --> 00:11:38,820
In just a few days,

93
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:41,100
you've been able to break the restriction spells.

94
00:11:42,670 --> 00:11:43,940
I value talent.

95
00:11:45,360 --> 00:11:46,820
But if your mind is distracted

96
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:48,100
and your conduct is improper,

97
00:11:48,750 --> 00:11:50,580
Yaoguang Peak will not keep you.

98
00:11:52,790 --> 00:11:53,650
I know my mistake.

99
00:12:04,740 --> 00:12:06,250
This is the Danxue secret realm.

100
00:12:07,340 --> 00:12:09,730
Only disciples who have reached the third level of cultivation

101
00:12:09,750 --> 00:12:10,700
can leave here.

102
00:12:11,860 --> 00:12:14,530
What you learned before was broad but not focused.

103
00:12:14,980 --> 00:12:16,420
Your spirit aura is chaotic.

104
00:12:16,910 --> 00:12:18,940
If you can't let go of greed and worldly attachments

105
00:12:19,340 --> 00:12:20,420
and purify your spirit and essence,

106
00:12:21,550 --> 00:12:23,060
you will stay in there for the rest of your life.

107
00:12:48,150 --> 00:12:48,940
Gather the Qi in the vessel

108
00:12:49,270 --> 00:12:50,060
and merge it with heaven and earth.

109
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:50,940
Transform Qi into spirit

110
00:12:50,960 --> 00:12:51,850
and command all things!

111
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:14,700
Among Wuyue Court's sixteen peaks,

112
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:15,940
there is no Hushe Peak.

113
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:17,770
Right.

114
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:19,420
None of us has ever seen Hushe Peak.

115
00:13:19,960 --> 00:13:20,580
Lifei,

116
00:13:20,790 --> 00:13:21,940
where did you hear about it?

117
00:13:23,870 --> 00:13:25,980
I've searched every peak

118
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:27,130
and couldn't find my senior brother.

119
00:13:27,150 --> 00:13:28,060
I'm getting anxious.

120
00:13:28,870 --> 00:13:29,700
Come here.

121
00:13:29,750 --> 00:13:30,180
Here.

122
00:13:31,630 --> 00:13:32,770
Besides

123
00:13:33,390 --> 00:13:35,130
the southwest corner of Baicao Peak,

124
00:13:35,150 --> 00:13:36,530
are there any other peaks?

125
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:39,460
Never seen one.

126
00:13:40,960 --> 00:13:41,490
Oh,

127
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:43,370
you haven't been to Cuihua Peak yet, right?

128
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:47,770
It has never allowed unauthorized entry by disciples of other peaks.

129
00:13:48,150 --> 00:13:50,700
If you want Elder Cuixuan to use Lifei to temper his sword,

130
00:13:50,870 --> 00:13:52,340
by all means, encourage her to go.

131
00:13:58,150 --> 00:13:59,370
The third level of Wuyue Court's techniques.

132
00:14:00,150 --> 00:14:01,060
Spirit energy floods the meridians;

133
00:14:01,840 --> 00:14:02,820
cultivator and sword become one.

134
00:14:14,480 --> 00:14:15,530
The Danxue secret realm

135
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:17,370
is actually a state of mind.

136
00:14:18,550 --> 00:14:19,490
Unless the inner demon is removed,

137
00:14:19,750 --> 00:14:20,700
the formation will never break.

138
00:14:46,200 --> 00:14:46,980
Inner demon?

139
00:15:07,720 --> 00:15:08,180
Kill.

140
00:15:39,630 --> 00:15:41,770
Did Lei Xiuyuan get punished by his master?

141
00:15:45,080 --> 00:15:45,890
None of my business.

142
00:15:46,150 --> 00:15:46,770
Don't think about him.

143
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:07,940
The technique is incomplete.

144
00:16:08,910 --> 00:16:09,850
She will still feel pain.

145
00:16:25,080 --> 00:16:27,980
To walk the world is to hold a torch through endless night.

146
00:16:28,790 --> 00:16:30,180
Your goodwill still lingers,

147
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:31,890
and you are bold and resolute,

148
00:16:32,240 --> 00:16:33,340
so you may break free from this deadlock.

149
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:35,980
Remember, what your soul yearns for

150
00:16:36,360 --> 00:16:38,300
is the right path for you.

151
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:40,180
What my soul yearns for?

152
00:17:06,830 --> 00:17:08,810
I was right about you.

153
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:11,220
You've broken through the third level.

154
00:17:11,790 --> 00:17:14,490
You must have found your heart of cultivation.

155
00:17:15,550 --> 00:17:16,090
Remember,

156
00:17:16,720 --> 00:17:18,570
this heart can overturn heaven and earth.

157
00:17:19,070 --> 00:17:20,620
Even if faced with thunder, fire,

158
00:17:20,880 --> 00:17:21,940
and endless calamity,

159
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:24,660
it can't be shaken.

160
00:17:35,270 --> 00:17:36,090
- Hello. - Hello.

161
00:17:37,350 --> 00:17:39,330
Heard he broke through the third level in just three days.

162
00:17:39,830 --> 00:17:40,570
Truly impressive.

163
00:17:40,920 --> 00:17:42,010
No wonder Master values him

164
00:17:42,110 --> 00:17:42,940
and took him as a direct disciple.

165
00:17:43,270 --> 00:17:44,460
Truly gifted.

166
00:17:44,590 --> 00:17:45,180
Indeed.

167
00:17:46,590 --> 00:17:47,420
Congratulations

168
00:17:47,720 --> 00:17:48,490
on your advancement.

169
00:17:48,830 --> 00:17:50,290
You've broken through the third level.

170
00:17:50,720 --> 00:17:51,530
Before you,

171
00:17:51,750 --> 00:17:53,980
only Hu Jiaping had done it.

172
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:55,700
That traitor!

173
00:17:56,790 --> 00:17:58,220
Bewitched by an artifact spirit,

174
00:17:58,350 --> 00:18:00,330
he lost his mind and defied Master.

175
00:18:00,480 --> 00:18:02,900
He's brought shame to Yaoguang Peak.

176
00:18:03,590 --> 00:18:04,570
Well said.

177
00:18:05,160 --> 00:18:05,770
Right.

178
00:18:08,590 --> 00:18:10,330
Hu was Master's direct disciple.

179
00:18:10,640 --> 00:18:11,730
He entered before you.

180
00:18:12,480 --> 00:18:13,420
Speaking ill of your senior

181
00:18:13,830 --> 00:18:14,770
is the same as insulting our master.

182
00:18:16,310 --> 00:18:17,760
[Songfeng, Wuyue Court]
So what if you broke through

183
00:18:17,760 --> 00:18:18,490
the third level?

184
00:18:19,240 --> 00:18:21,810
You must have used some magical treasure, right?

185
00:18:22,440 --> 00:18:24,220
Fine. I'll show you.

186
00:18:32,440 --> 00:18:33,290
Songfeng,

187
00:18:33,790 --> 00:18:34,770
you've been here for years

188
00:18:34,790 --> 00:18:36,140
and still haven't broken through the second level.

189
00:18:36,240 --> 00:18:37,530
Master is already disappointed.

190
00:18:38,030 --> 00:18:40,380
I suggest you watch your words.

191
00:18:41,070 --> 00:18:43,290
Don't upset him further.

192
00:18:43,310 --> 00:18:43,770
You...

193
00:18:48,070 --> 00:18:48,490
Go!

194
00:18:49,960 --> 00:18:50,570
Stop staring!

195
00:18:55,510 --> 00:18:56,900
Songfeng holds grudges.

196
00:18:57,110 --> 00:18:58,530
He probably won't let this go.

197
00:18:59,640 --> 00:19:00,220
Let him.

198
00:19:01,550 --> 00:19:04,420
I thought you had issues with Hu.

199
00:19:04,960 --> 00:19:06,140
Didn't expect you to defend him.

200
00:19:10,200 --> 00:19:11,140
He taught us.

201
00:19:12,350 --> 00:19:13,140
Us?

202
00:19:15,550 --> 00:19:16,290
Jiang Lifei?

203
00:19:27,270 --> 00:19:28,380
Crispy skin, tender meat.

204
00:19:28,550 --> 00:19:29,810
Looks delicious.

205
00:19:30,070 --> 00:19:30,700
Where is Hushe Peak?

206
00:19:33,510 --> 00:19:34,140
Tell me!

207
00:19:34,440 --> 00:19:35,900
I suddenly remembered something.

208
00:19:36,160 --> 00:19:37,730
I have to go right now.

209
00:19:38,750 --> 00:19:39,140
Wait,

210
00:19:39,440 --> 00:19:39,940
can you...?

211
00:19:47,480 --> 00:19:48,220
Master,

212
00:19:48,920 --> 00:19:50,330
when will you be back?

213
00:19:51,350 --> 00:19:53,420
I... I don't know exactly.

214
00:19:53,460 --> 00:19:55,700
But you behave and listen to Zhaomin while I'm gone.

215
00:19:57,830 --> 00:19:59,980
What shameful secret is hidden in there?

216
00:20:00,310 --> 00:20:01,980
Who says Hushe Peak has a secret to...?

217
00:20:05,940 --> 00:20:08,010
There really is a Hushe Peak, isn't there?

218
00:20:09,070 --> 00:20:09,860
Actually,

219
00:20:10,110 --> 00:20:11,330
I know where it is.

220
00:20:11,830 --> 00:20:14,010
There's a map of it in Huanyue Shrine.

221
00:20:14,420 --> 00:20:15,380
Fine.

222
00:20:15,660 --> 00:20:16,460
I guess

223
00:20:16,550 --> 00:20:18,290
no one here can control you anymore.

224
00:20:18,500 --> 00:20:20,420
You've even gone to Huanyue Shrine!

225
00:20:22,700 --> 00:20:23,980
If you won't tell me,

226
00:20:25,070 --> 00:20:26,220
then I'll go myself.

227
00:20:26,260 --> 00:20:27,420
Go ahead then.

228
00:20:27,460 --> 00:20:28,420
It has a restriction spell.

229
00:20:28,460 --> 00:20:29,900
You think you can get in?

230
00:20:30,260 --> 00:20:31,010
Restriction spell?

231
00:20:31,750 --> 00:20:32,530
So mysterious.

232
00:20:35,270 --> 00:20:36,460
Could it be...?

233
00:20:39,750 --> 00:20:41,490
What do you know?

234
00:20:44,420 --> 00:20:45,330
Is there treasure in there?

235
00:20:46,220 --> 00:20:47,220
What treasure, Master?

236
00:20:47,260 --> 00:20:48,050
How much is it worth?

237
00:20:48,180 --> 00:20:50,250
A girl shouldn't be so vulgar.

238
00:20:50,700 --> 00:20:51,620
We'll talk when I get back.

239
00:20:54,740 --> 00:20:55,530
Master.

240
00:20:55,700 --> 00:20:56,490
Tell me now.

241
00:20:56,510 --> 00:20:58,250
Tell me now.

242
00:20:59,660 --> 00:21:01,290
This is urgent.

243
00:21:01,310 --> 00:21:01,980
I'm off!

244
00:21:04,900 --> 00:21:05,730
Master!

245
00:21:06,790 --> 00:21:07,460
Master.

246
00:21:17,790 --> 00:21:19,290
Zhaomin's three-sided mirror.

247
00:21:19,460 --> 00:21:20,860
Master's six-sided mirror.

248
00:21:21,270 --> 00:21:23,490
They should be able to help me break the restriction spell.

249
00:21:57,310 --> 00:21:59,330
Hushe Peak looks like a mallet.

250
00:22:36,550 --> 00:22:37,250
Mr. Hu?

251
00:22:37,790 --> 00:22:38,620
What are you doing here?

252
00:22:39,700 --> 00:22:40,420
Stop looking.

253
00:22:42,070 --> 00:22:43,420
I am your senior brother.

254
00:22:49,980 --> 00:22:50,770
Hold tight.

255
00:22:51,420 --> 00:22:52,220
Or you'll fall.

256
00:22:57,220 --> 00:22:58,140
Senior Brother?

257
00:23:02,030 --> 00:23:03,530
You're really my senior brother?

258
00:23:04,510 --> 00:23:06,090
The one in Master's sketch?

259
00:23:07,350 --> 00:23:08,140
Don't mention that sketch.

260
00:23:08,270 --> 00:23:10,770
I'm handsome and elegant.

261
00:23:11,420 --> 00:23:12,530
I look nowhere near that ugly.

262
00:23:13,940 --> 00:23:15,250
Senior Brother!

263
00:23:15,830 --> 00:23:17,570
Why did you only show up now?

264
00:23:18,180 --> 00:23:19,810
I've been looking for you forever!

265
00:23:23,260 --> 00:23:24,730
You got snot all over my new clothes.

266
00:23:25,020 --> 00:23:26,700
Mu made this for me.

267
00:23:26,900 --> 00:23:27,980
Look at the mess you made.

268
00:23:30,510 --> 00:23:31,700
You're really my senior brother?

269
00:23:32,790 --> 00:23:33,770
Would I lie to you?

270
00:23:35,830 --> 00:23:37,010
Listen to me.

271
00:23:37,030 --> 00:23:38,420
I still can't believe it.

272
00:23:40,220 --> 00:23:41,980
I was an orphan too, just like you.

273
00:23:43,260 --> 00:23:44,490
After that old man took me in,

274
00:23:45,070 --> 00:23:46,980
I followed him, wandering from place to place.

275
00:23:47,790 --> 00:23:49,090
When I grew older

276
00:23:49,660 --> 00:23:51,290
and had learned most of his skills,

277
00:23:51,900 --> 00:23:53,490
he sent me to Chufeng Academy.

278
00:23:54,270 --> 00:23:56,860
Later, I gained the favor of Master Guangwei,

279
00:23:57,070 --> 00:23:58,050
so I went to Wuyue Court.

280
00:23:58,590 --> 00:23:59,660
And you probably know

281
00:24:00,220 --> 00:24:01,220
the rest.

282
00:24:02,740 --> 00:24:04,770
Then why didn't you tell me when I asked before?

283
00:24:05,110 --> 00:24:06,140
You even made things hard for me.

284
00:24:07,420 --> 00:24:08,660
I had no choice.

285
00:24:09,030 --> 00:24:10,420
Master said

286
00:24:10,660 --> 00:24:12,530
I could never mention this to anyone.

287
00:24:13,420 --> 00:24:15,700
Otherwise, both he and I would lose our lives.

288
00:24:16,220 --> 00:24:16,810
And

289
00:24:17,030 --> 00:24:18,250
when did I ever make things hard for you?

290
00:24:18,500 --> 00:24:20,980
That was encouragement and motivation.

291
00:24:21,070 --> 00:24:23,380
I meant well.

292
00:24:24,030 --> 00:24:25,220
I think you had bad intentions.

293
00:24:25,590 --> 00:24:26,810
You just wanted to kick me out of the academy!

294
00:24:27,310 --> 00:24:28,090
You wronged me.

295
00:24:28,510 --> 00:24:30,010
I never wanted to kick you out.

296
00:24:30,220 --> 00:24:31,980
The one I wanted to get rid of was Lei Xiuyuan.

297
00:24:34,220 --> 00:24:34,810
Why?

298
00:24:38,460 --> 00:24:39,090
Because...

299
00:24:40,270 --> 00:24:42,180
Because he clearly doesn't look like a good guy.

300
00:24:42,510 --> 00:24:43,770
I have sharp eyes.

301
00:24:43,790 --> 00:24:45,810
I could tell he had ulterior motives toward you.

302
00:24:46,110 --> 00:24:47,010
See?

303
00:24:47,030 --> 00:24:48,090
You didn't listen

304
00:24:48,110 --> 00:24:48,660
to your elder.

305
00:24:48,900 --> 00:24:50,050
Almost got yourself killed, didn't you?

306
00:24:59,680 --> 00:25:00,220
No.

307
00:25:01,000 --> 00:25:01,530
That's not right.

308
00:25:02,400 --> 00:25:03,620
You're definitely hiding something else from me.

309
00:25:04,110 --> 00:25:05,460
No, really.

310
00:25:05,480 --> 00:25:06,940
Don't overthink things.

311
00:25:07,240 --> 00:25:08,330
You love causing trouble, too.

312
00:25:08,480 --> 00:25:09,420
If it weren't for you,

313
00:25:09,640 --> 00:25:10,250
I wouldn't be

314
00:25:10,270 --> 00:25:11,620
at Wuyue Court this late.

315
00:25:11,680 --> 00:25:12,220
Right?

316
00:25:15,480 --> 00:25:16,050
Jiaping,

317
00:25:16,440 --> 00:25:17,700
do you know where Master is?

318
00:25:18,400 --> 00:25:19,570
Is he being hunted?

319
00:25:20,000 --> 00:25:20,980
Is his life in danger?

320
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:24,770
Master is a hidden expert.

321
00:25:25,310 --> 00:25:26,730
Ordinary people can't touch him.

322
00:25:27,720 --> 00:25:28,420
An expert?

323
00:25:29,680 --> 00:25:31,090
Why would an expert go into hiding?

324
00:25:34,680 --> 00:25:36,010
He's not some bandit, is he?

325
00:25:37,480 --> 00:25:38,420
Maybe he has too many enemies?

326
00:25:40,070 --> 00:25:40,980
Can't you wish

327
00:25:41,000 --> 00:25:42,980
for something good for our master?

328
00:25:43,640 --> 00:25:45,180
He must have his reasons

329
00:25:45,310 --> 00:25:46,660
for going into hiding.

330
00:25:47,240 --> 00:25:48,530
If you keep looking around blindly,

331
00:25:48,680 --> 00:25:50,570
you'll only bring trouble. Understand?

332
00:25:51,480 --> 00:25:52,330
No.

333
00:25:52,750 --> 00:25:54,490
I need to see with my own eyes that he's safe.

334
00:25:55,200 --> 00:25:56,180
Fine, fine.

335
00:25:56,480 --> 00:25:58,460
I'll find him.

336
00:25:58,790 --> 00:26:01,140
Your top priority now is to focus on your cultivation.

337
00:26:01,680 --> 00:26:03,530
Now that you've become Master Chongyi's disciple,

338
00:26:03,960 --> 00:26:05,090
study hard under him.

339
00:26:05,400 --> 00:26:06,940
Otherwise, even if you find Master,

340
00:26:07,350 --> 00:26:08,530
with your current skills,

341
00:26:08,830 --> 00:26:09,940
you won't be able to help him anyway.

342
00:26:11,720 --> 00:26:14,570
Is that why Master didn't tell me?

343
00:26:14,590 --> 00:26:15,860
Because I can't help?

344
00:26:18,790 --> 00:26:19,380
Jiaping.

345
00:26:20,110 --> 00:26:20,900
I need to get stronger.

346
00:26:21,310 --> 00:26:22,900
One day, I'll be able to help Master.

347
00:26:23,070 --> 00:26:23,660
Good.

348
00:26:25,480 --> 00:26:26,730
Since you show such devotion,

349
00:26:27,070 --> 00:26:29,620
I'll help you.

350
00:26:38,110 --> 00:26:39,770
Your constitution is unique.

351
00:26:40,590 --> 00:26:41,810
So you don't have to follow

352
00:26:42,200 --> 00:26:43,730
the usual methods of cultivation.

353
00:26:44,550 --> 00:26:45,250
Remember,

354
00:26:46,200 --> 00:26:47,250
all spirit energy

355
00:26:47,510 --> 00:26:49,570
is within your every breath.

356
00:26:50,240 --> 00:26:52,810
Nothing is everything. Emptiness is fullness.

357
00:27:11,240 --> 00:27:12,900
Even a flying insect has its own path.

358
00:27:13,750 --> 00:27:14,290
Lifei,

359
00:27:14,880 --> 00:27:16,330
you have a long road ahead.

360
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:18,140
You'll understand it in time.

361
00:27:18,680 --> 00:27:21,900
Not a word to anyone about what happened today.

362
00:27:25,000 --> 00:27:25,940
I felt it.

363
00:27:26,590 --> 00:27:27,700
Such pure spirit energy.

364
00:27:28,310 --> 00:27:28,730
Jiaping...

365
00:27:34,510 --> 00:27:35,050
Jiaping!

366
00:27:36,590 --> 00:27:37,700
I'm going back to the academy.

367
00:27:38,030 --> 00:27:39,330
Here's the Mind-Calming Mantra for you.

368
00:27:40,270 --> 00:27:41,530
Stay calm through all changes.

369
00:27:42,160 --> 00:27:43,860
Keep your spirit steady and your mind clear.

370
00:27:48,440 --> 00:27:49,860
Just like Master's disciple.

371
00:27:50,110 --> 00:27:51,570
Leaves a letter and disappears. Same bad habit!

372
00:27:55,030 --> 00:27:55,460
Wait,

373
00:27:56,790 --> 00:27:57,770
I don't know the way back!

374
00:27:58,200 --> 00:27:59,490
At least take me back first!

375
00:28:00,200 --> 00:28:00,810
Jiaping.

376
00:28:01,510 --> 00:28:02,810
I don't know the way.

377
00:28:03,270 --> 00:28:04,010
Jiaping!

378
00:28:05,790 --> 00:28:07,700
Jiaping!

379
00:28:13,000 --> 00:28:15,290
Is Zhuiyu Peak to the east or west?

380
00:28:24,270 --> 00:28:25,050
Lifei.

381
00:28:30,200 --> 00:28:30,900
Lifei,

382
00:28:31,880 --> 00:28:32,660
it's you?

383
00:28:32,790 --> 00:28:33,900
Qin?

384
00:28:34,070 --> 00:28:34,810
You're back?

385
00:28:36,880 --> 00:28:37,730
Stop following me.

386
00:28:39,680 --> 00:28:41,490
Aren't you Master Chongyi's disciple?

387
00:28:41,920 --> 00:28:43,050
Why are you here at night?

388
00:28:44,880 --> 00:28:47,140
Are you lost?

389
00:28:48,200 --> 00:28:48,860
Yes.

390
00:28:49,720 --> 00:28:51,810
I thought the moonlight was beautiful

391
00:28:52,400 --> 00:28:53,940
and just wanted to fly in for a closer look.

392
00:28:54,240 --> 00:28:55,810
But the wind was howling,

393
00:28:55,830 --> 00:28:56,660
and I got dizzy

394
00:28:56,680 --> 00:28:57,810
and ended up here.

395
00:28:58,270 --> 00:28:59,090
Wuyue Court

396
00:28:59,310 --> 00:29:00,570
has strong winds and thick fog at night.

397
00:29:00,920 --> 00:29:02,090
Each peak has its own restriction spell.

398
00:29:02,310 --> 00:29:02,980
You can't wander around.

399
00:29:05,830 --> 00:29:07,570
How about I take you back to Zhuiyu Peak?

400
00:29:08,640 --> 00:29:09,530
Okay. Please.

401
00:29:09,790 --> 00:29:11,290
Thank you so much.

402
00:29:19,160 --> 00:29:19,700
Hold tight.

403
00:29:31,920 --> 00:29:33,490
Lifei doesn't trust others easily.

404
00:29:35,110 --> 00:29:36,330
I was worrying for nothing.

405
00:29:54,070 --> 00:29:54,530
Hold tight.

406
00:30:21,440 --> 00:30:23,330
Remember now.

407
00:30:25,680 --> 00:30:26,250
Lifei!

408
00:30:32,720 --> 00:30:33,770
Why those images?

409
00:30:34,880 --> 00:30:35,980
And whose voice was that?

410
00:31:02,640 --> 00:31:03,290
Lifei.

411
00:31:04,110 --> 00:31:04,620
Lifei!

412
00:31:05,440 --> 00:31:06,180
Lifei.

413
00:31:07,030 --> 00:31:07,730
Jiang Lifei!

414
00:31:08,200 --> 00:31:08,570
Jiang...

415
00:31:24,750 --> 00:31:25,730
What's wrong with her?

416
00:31:26,240 --> 00:31:27,180
What's going on here?

417
00:31:28,400 --> 00:31:30,090
Lifei started training at dawn.

418
00:31:30,790 --> 00:31:34,090
Is she finally turning over a new leaf?

419
00:31:37,400 --> 00:31:39,220
No way. Absolutely not.

420
00:31:40,480 --> 00:31:42,860
Jiang Lifei, stop pretending.

421
00:31:44,160 --> 00:31:46,620
Master. You know what?

422
00:31:46,880 --> 00:31:48,530
If it weren't for Qin bringing me back

423
00:31:48,550 --> 00:31:49,380
yesterday,

424
00:31:49,400 --> 00:31:51,090
I might never have seen you again.

425
00:31:52,160 --> 00:31:54,180
If I'm so useless,

426
00:31:54,350 --> 00:31:55,900
that would embarrass you.

427
00:31:56,550 --> 00:31:57,860
For your honor

428
00:31:58,640 --> 00:32:00,660
and for Zhuiyu Peak's dignity,

429
00:32:00,920 --> 00:32:03,050
won't you teach me some self-defense techniques?

430
00:32:04,160 --> 00:32:04,980
Then you...

431
00:32:05,240 --> 00:32:08,940
Um, I'll make you meat buns.

432
00:32:10,070 --> 00:32:12,220
Fine. I'll teach you one.

433
00:32:13,550 --> 00:32:15,220
But let's be clear. Whether you make it or not

434
00:32:15,680 --> 00:32:16,620
depends on you.

435
00:32:20,350 --> 00:32:22,010
Don't just stand there. Go make the food.

436
00:32:22,880 --> 00:32:24,460
Right away. Just a moment.

437
00:32:29,510 --> 00:32:31,290
I went to the place they mentioned last time.

438
00:32:31,790 --> 00:32:32,620
I liked it too.

439
00:32:37,790 --> 00:32:38,660
Lei Xiuyuan!

440
00:32:40,510 --> 00:32:42,700
They say you're Wuyue Court's

441
00:32:42,720 --> 00:32:44,050
once-in-a-century genius.

442
00:32:44,270 --> 00:32:46,490
Since we're both free today,

443
00:32:48,590 --> 00:32:50,220
how about a spar?

444
00:32:52,440 --> 00:32:53,180
Stop right there!

445
00:33:12,200 --> 00:33:13,250
You dare destroy my sword?

446
00:33:18,960 --> 00:33:21,050
Lei, we're fellow disciples.

447
00:33:21,240 --> 00:33:22,050
Let's keep things friendly.

448
00:33:22,550 --> 00:33:23,730
Qin.

449
00:33:27,240 --> 00:33:27,770
Qin.

450
00:33:28,680 --> 00:33:30,140
It's been half a year since we parted at the academy.

451
00:33:30,510 --> 00:33:31,220
I heard

452
00:33:31,240 --> 00:33:32,940
Master Guangwei took you as his personal disciple.

453
00:33:33,200 --> 00:33:33,860
Congratulations.

454
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:35,770
It's just my master's favor.

455
00:33:36,480 --> 00:33:38,180
Qin, I have things to do.

456
00:33:38,350 --> 00:33:39,140
I'm leaving.

457
00:33:45,240 --> 00:33:46,290
Look at him, so smug.

458
00:33:47,030 --> 00:33:47,810
He struts around

459
00:33:47,830 --> 00:33:49,380
just because he broke through the third level

460
00:33:49,480 --> 00:33:50,620
at Danxue.

461
00:33:51,030 --> 00:33:52,810
He doesn't even respect Qin.

462
00:33:54,640 --> 00:33:57,620
Qin, you're known for your exceptional talent.

463
00:33:57,830 --> 00:34:00,250
You're about to break through the fifth level.

464
00:34:01,440 --> 00:34:03,220
Having a rising star like Lei

465
00:34:03,270 --> 00:34:04,460
is a blessing for Wuyue Court.

466
00:34:05,070 --> 00:34:07,290
Songfeng, I need to see Master Guangwei.

467
00:34:07,440 --> 00:34:08,130
I'm leaving.

468
00:34:11,280 --> 00:34:12,570
If it weren't for Qin,

469
00:34:13,030 --> 00:34:14,130
I'd have taught him a lesson.

470
00:34:25,400 --> 00:34:27,300
Wu Nuo is just an outer sect disciple.

471
00:34:28,000 --> 00:34:29,740
He is of low cultivation, utterly insignificant.

472
00:34:30,480 --> 00:34:32,050
Why did it take you so long

473
00:34:32,070 --> 00:34:33,170
to subdue him?

474
00:34:33,670 --> 00:34:36,610
Sir, that traitor was secretly practicing demonic techniques.

475
00:34:36,920 --> 00:34:37,860
He went mad

476
00:34:38,070 --> 00:34:39,490
and killed his fellow disciples.

477
00:34:39,880 --> 00:34:41,570
He absorbed their spirit power,

478
00:34:41,960 --> 00:34:43,690
which greatly boosted his cultivation.

479
00:34:44,400 --> 00:34:46,090
I had to use my master's

480
00:34:46,110 --> 00:34:47,090
Yin-Yang Tribulation Mirror

481
00:34:47,230 --> 00:34:48,780
to barely restrain him.

482
00:34:49,440 --> 00:34:52,490
How could an immortal sect disciple know demonic techniques?

483
00:34:53,000 --> 00:34:54,090
Have you found out why?

484
00:35:02,760 --> 00:35:06,820
There's no right or wrong in techniques. Power is the only truth.

485
00:35:09,150 --> 00:35:12,300
Think it over. You can hand it in

486
00:35:13,360 --> 00:35:15,010
or not.

487
00:35:16,320 --> 00:35:18,860
I searched for days but found nothing.

488
00:35:20,030 --> 00:35:23,380
Perhaps he was bewitched by the demons.

489
00:35:23,840 --> 00:35:25,210
I've heard of similar incidents

490
00:35:25,230 --> 00:35:26,650
occurring in other sects.

491
00:35:27,000 --> 00:35:30,460
It seems the demons want to overthrow the Central Plains

492
00:35:30,960 --> 00:35:31,980
and divide the immortal sects.

493
00:35:34,440 --> 00:35:35,530
That's possible.

494
00:35:36,110 --> 00:35:37,650
Demons have always been cunning.

495
00:35:38,440 --> 00:35:39,900
With the Sea Calamity approaching,

496
00:35:40,280 --> 00:35:42,420
they will send spies to infiltrate the Central Plains,

497
00:35:42,920 --> 00:35:45,210
spreading confusion and causing trouble.

498
00:35:45,840 --> 00:35:46,300
Yangling,

499
00:35:46,840 --> 00:35:47,980
gather the disciples immediately.

500
00:35:48,280 --> 00:35:49,650
Set up the Demon-Quelling Formation

501
00:35:50,550 --> 00:35:52,130
to secure Wuyue Court.

502
00:35:52,760 --> 00:35:53,340
Also,

503
00:35:53,800 --> 00:35:55,980
strictly screen all inner and outer sect disciples.

504
00:35:56,070 --> 00:35:57,010
Strengthen our defenses.

505
00:35:57,480 --> 00:35:59,460
We mustn't give the demons any opening.

506
00:36:00,150 --> 00:36:00,650
Yes.

507
00:36:14,190 --> 00:36:14,780
Master,

508
00:36:15,360 --> 00:36:16,340
Master Guangwei suspects

509
00:36:16,360 --> 00:36:17,530
it was a demon spy.

510
00:36:17,710 --> 00:36:19,860
He's ordered all peaks to be on high alert against infiltrators.

511
00:36:52,880 --> 00:36:54,090
After all this time,

512
00:36:54,630 --> 00:36:57,530
you still haven't broken through the fifth level.

513
00:36:57,840 --> 00:36:59,300
Useless.

514
00:36:59,710 --> 00:37:02,260
You probably can't even withstand a single strike from the demons.

515
00:37:02,960 --> 00:37:05,780
How can you lead the sect against the Sea Calamity?

516
00:37:07,190 --> 00:37:08,650
How can I possibly

517
00:37:08,880 --> 00:37:11,170
entrust Wuyue Court to your hands?

518
00:37:13,480 --> 00:37:14,300
I am deeply ashamed.

519
00:37:14,670 --> 00:37:16,530
Only the strong may remain on Cuihua Peak.

520
00:37:17,030 --> 00:37:18,610
If you show no improvement,

521
00:37:19,360 --> 00:37:21,690
step down for the younger disciples.

522
00:37:22,440 --> 00:37:23,010
Yes.

523
00:37:27,000 --> 00:37:29,460
Scatter into wind, gather into form.

524
00:37:29,480 --> 00:37:31,090
Draw the essence of heaven and earth,

525
00:37:31,280 --> 00:37:34,380
and fuse the five elemental powers of metal, wood, water, fire, and earth

526
00:37:34,400 --> 00:37:35,380
into your vessel.

527
00:37:36,230 --> 00:37:39,050
Release different techniques according to subtle variations,

528
00:37:39,070 --> 00:37:41,210
and you will have endless transformations.

529
00:37:41,800 --> 00:37:45,650
This is the Earth-Shattering Five Turtles Technique.

530
00:38:22,880 --> 00:38:24,780
Master! Did you see that?

531
00:38:25,360 --> 00:38:26,490
I can use the water technique now.

532
00:38:29,880 --> 00:38:30,650
Well...

533
00:38:31,400 --> 00:38:32,460
I taught you for so long,

534
00:38:32,480 --> 00:38:35,010
and you've only just managed to fuse your water and wood spirits.

535
00:38:35,550 --> 00:38:37,050
I'm a bit ashamed, honestly.

536
00:38:37,510 --> 00:38:38,490
The hard part is still ahead.

537
00:38:38,800 --> 00:38:41,460
Especially the metal technique. That's the foremost of the five elements.

538
00:38:42,000 --> 00:38:42,780
Take your time practicing.

539
00:38:44,150 --> 00:38:45,300
As I always say,

540
00:38:45,440 --> 00:38:47,090
I've taught you everything.

541
00:38:47,670 --> 00:38:49,490
Whether you succeed is all up to you.

542
00:39:00,480 --> 00:39:02,340
Where... where did it go?

543
00:39:05,280 --> 00:39:06,210
Where did it go?

544
00:39:07,360 --> 00:39:08,460
What happened, Master?

545
00:39:15,320 --> 00:39:16,380
Take your time practicing.

546
00:39:16,960 --> 00:39:18,260
I'm going back to sleep.

547
00:39:24,190 --> 00:39:26,130
Practice all you want, but don't forget to cook.

548
00:39:26,920 --> 00:39:27,650
Got it.

549
00:39:28,110 --> 00:39:29,380
You're still eating while you talk.

550
00:39:55,320 --> 00:39:57,010
How am I supposed to use this metal spirit?

551
00:40:34,400 --> 00:40:34,690
I...

552
00:40:35,400 --> 00:40:36,650
I mastered the metal technique?

553
00:41:34,760 --> 00:41:38,440
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

554
00:41:38,760 --> 00:41:41,260
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

555
00:41:41,720 --> 00:41:45,040
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

556
00:41:45,280 --> 00:41:47,480
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

557
00:41:48,520 --> 00:41:52,000
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

558
00:41:52,720 --> 00:41:55,080
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

559
00:41:55,680 --> 00:41:57,200
♪No calamity can rival♪

560
00:41:57,600 --> 00:42:00,640
♪The lingering thread of a fragrance♪

561
00:42:02,780 --> 00:42:06,260
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

562
00:42:07,020 --> 00:42:09,260
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

563
00:42:10,070 --> 00:42:11,010
What do you want?

564
00:42:11,010 --> 00:42:12,740
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

565
00:42:13,380 --> 00:42:15,660
♪Past the pagoda♪

566
00:42:16,460 --> 00:42:18,510
♪In fine robes on galloping horses♪

567
00:42:18,510 --> 00:42:19,210
Your spirit energy.

568
00:42:20,300 --> 00:42:22,580
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

569
00:42:23,100 --> 00:42:26,060
♪Betrayed by all, I still♪

570
00:42:26,780 --> 00:42:28,980
♪Reign supreme♪

571
00:42:30,060 --> 00:42:33,200
